    27Рєњ### Server options
    29РєњThe `serve` hostname defaults to `localhost`, and the port defaults to `3000`. Either option can be specified on the command line:
    30Рєњ
    31Рєњ```bash
    32Рєњmdbook serve path/to/book -p 8000 -n 127.0.0.1 
    33Рєњ```
