for_developers/preprocessors.md
     1Рєњ# Preprocessors
     3РєњA *preprocessor* is simply a bit of code which gets run immediately after the
     4Рєњbook is loaded and before it gets rendered, allowing you to update and mutate
     5Рєњthe book. Possible use cases are:
     6Рєњ
     7Рєњ- Creating custom helpers like `\{{#include /path/to/file.md}}`
     8Рєњ- Substituting in latex-style expressions (`$$ \frac{1}{3} $$`) with their
     9Рєњ  mathjax equivalents
    10Рєњ
      РєњРђд
    13Рєњ## Hooking into MDBook Рђд
    46Рєњ## Hints for implementing a preprocessor Рђд
    74Рєњ## Implementing a preprocessor with a different language Рђд
